s 乐队发起的请愿书中得到强调，此后签名的音乐家包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kneecap">Kneecap</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lambrini-girls">Lambrini Girls</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/alfie-templeman">Alfie Templeman</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lip-critic">Lip Critic</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/wunderhorse">Wunderhorse</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mary-in-the-junkyard">Mary In The Junkyard</a> 。</p><p>上个月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">由于音乐节与巴克莱银行的联系，Cherym 退出了 The Great Escape</a> ，之后唱片公司<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cherym-pull-out-of-the-great-escape-festival-due-to-its-links-with-barclays-bank-3617202">Alcopop 和 Big Scary Monsters 也</a>加入了抵制并退出了该活动。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dozens-more-artists-join-great-escape-2024-boycott-as-half-the-line-up-demands-festival-drop-barclays-sponsor-in-solidarity-with-palestine-3619074">很快，又有数十个表演团体纷纷效仿</a>，其中超过一半的表演团体要求 The Great Escape 放弃与巴克莱银行的赞助协议。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/idles">IDLES</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/squid">Squid</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/massive-attack">Massive Attack</a>等超过 1,200 名艺术家也<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dozens-more-artists-join-great-escape-2024-boycott-as-half-the-line-up-demands-festival-drop-barclays-sponsor-in-solidarity-with-palestine-3619074">签署了一封致 The Great Escape 的公开信</a>，要求他们取消巴克莱的赞助资格。 “以色列继续无视国际法，无视联合国停火的呼吁，并阻止向加沙巴勒斯坦人提供援助，包括杀害援助人员。我们不能保持沉默。我们不会与“大逃亡<a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc5aXJrJnkeRTpEfdVgUvNYs6i4F_a8JzO6-yRuINlsqgwkVQ/viewform" target="_blank" rel="noopener">”</a>同谋，为巴克莱银行提供品牌推广机会。”</p><p>大逃亡尚未对<a href="https://www.instagram.com/bandsboycottbarclays/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">乐队抵制巴克莱</a>运动发表评论，而巴克莱则对最近的<a href="https://home.barclays/investor-relations/reports-and-events/general-meetings/agm-2024-faq/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">问答</a>环节中的回应提出了批评。巴克莱银行表示：“有人问我们为什么投资向以色列供货的九家国防公司，但这错误了我们的做法。” “作为一家银行，我们的工作是为数千名商业客户提供金融服务，其中包括国防部门的客户。”</p><p>与大逃亡罢工类似， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-cardinals-enola-gay-and-rachel-chinouriri-issue-statements-on-sxsw-2024-boycott-support-victims-of-war-3600184">许多艺术家拒绝参加 3 月份在德克萨斯州奥斯汀举行的 SXSW 音乐节，</a>因为该活动与以色列-加沙冲突期间的美国陆军和武器公司有联系。其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gruff-rhys-pulls-out-of-sxsw-in-protest-to-the-hyper-violence-inflicted-on-civilians-in-gaza-and-beyond-3601272">Gruff Rhys</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/kneecap-and-sprints-join-list-of-artists-boycotting-sxsw-2024-3599443">Kneecap、Sprints</a> 、Lambrini Girls、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/scowl-and-gel-pull-out-of-sxsw-we-refuse-to-participate-in-the-war-machine-3599056">Gel</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-cardinals-enola-gay-and-rachel-chinouriri-issue-statements-on-sxsw-2024-boycott-support-victims-of-war-3600184">Rachel Chinouriri</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-cardinals-enola-gay-and-rachel-chinouriri-issue-statements-on-sxsw-2024-boycott-support-victims-of-war-3600184">Cardinals</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/newdad-cardinals-enola-gay-and-rachel-chinouriri-issue-statements-on-sxsw-2024-boycott-support-victims-of-war-3600184">NewDad</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/soft-play-fka-slaves-drop-out-of-the-great-escape-2024-we-do-not-support-genocide-3756962">Soft Play – FKA Slaves – 退出《The Great Escape 2024》的帖子：“我们不支持种族灭绝”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
